C   TCONT(N)   - MOLECULAR CONTINUUM OPTICAL THICKNESS FOR LAYER N      FLX  550                                                         
C   TMOLS(N)   - RAYLEIGH SCATTERING OPTICAL THICKNESS FOR LAYER N      FLX  560                                                         
C   CSZEN(N)   - COSINE OF SOLAR ZENITH ANGLE FOR LAYER N               FLX  570                                                         
