C   S0         - SOLAR INTENSITY AT TOP OF ATMOSPHERE                   FLX  590                                                         
C   H1         - ALTITUDE OF OBSERVER (KM)                              FLX  600                                                         
C   H2         - ALTITUDE OF TARGET (KM)                                FLX  610                                                         
C   STRN(N)    - SOLAR TRANSMISSION TO BOTTOM OF LAYER N                FLX  620                                                         
