C   OUTPUT PARAMETERS:                                                  FLX  640                                                         
C   -----------------                                                   FLX  650                                                         
C   OMEGAK  (N)- SINGLE SCATTERING ALBEDO OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K     FLX  660                                                         
C   TAUM(K,N)  - MOLECULAR OPTICAL THICKNESS OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K  FLX  670                                                         
C   BTOP(N)    - BLACK BODY FLUX FOR UPPER EDGE TEMPERATURE OF LAYER N  FLX  680                                                         
C   BMID(N)    - BLACK BODY FLUX FOR AVERAGE TEMPERATURE OF LAYER N     FLX  690                                                         
C                                                                       FLX  700                                                         
C   INTERNAL PARAMETERS:                                                FLX  710                                                         
C   -------------------                                                 FLX  720                                                         
C   TWGP(K,N)  - SUM OF OPTICAL DEPTH * PROBABILITY BY MOLECULE         FLX  730                                                         
C                                                                       FLX  740                                                         
C   UPF(K,N)   - UPWARD THERMAL FLUX AT UPPER EDGE OF LAYER N FOR       FLX  750                                                         
C                VALUE OF K                                             FLX  760                                                         
C   UPFS(K,N)  - UPWARD SOLAR FLUX AT UPPER EDGE OF LAYER N FOR         FLX  770                                                         
C                VALUE OF K                                             FLX  780                                                         
C   DNF(K,N)   - DOWNWARD THERMAL FLUX AT UPPER EDGE OF LAYER N FOR     FLX  790                                                         
C                VALUE OF K                                             FLX  800                                                         
C   DNFS(K,N)  - DOWNWARD SOLAR FLUX AT UPPER EDGE OF LAYER N FOR       FLX  810                                                         
C                VALUE OF K                                             FLX  820                                                         
C   UMF(N)     - MEAN UPWARD THERMAL FLUX OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K     FLX  830                                                         
C   UMFS(N)    - MEAN UPWARD SOLAR FLUX OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K       FLX  840                                                         
C   DMF(N)     - MEAN DOWNWARD THERMAL FLUX OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K   FLX  850                                                         
C   DMFS(N)    - MEAN DOWNWARD SOLAR FLUX OF LAYER N FOR VALUE OF K     FLX  860                                                         
