C   SUS(K,N)   - UPWARD SOLAR RADIANCE SOURCE FUNCTION FOR N,K          FLX  880                                                         
C   SD(K,N)    - DOWNWARD THERMAL RADIANCE SOURCE FUNCTION FOR N,K      FLX  890                                                         
C   SDS(K,N)   - DOWNWARD SOLAR RADIANCE SOURCE FUNCTION FOR N,K        FLX  900                                                         
C   BETS(N)    - BACKSCATTER FRACTION ALONG SOLAR PATH AT LAYER N       FLX  910                                                         
C                                                                       FLX  920                                                         
C***********************************************************************FLX  930                                                         
C                                                                       FLX  940                                                         
C   NEW VARABLES          11 MOLECULES  BY JOSEPH H PIERLUISSI          FLX  950                                                         
C   DPWJ  PROBABILITY FOR EACH MOLECULE  FIT DOUBLE EXPODENTIAL         FLX  960                                                         
C   GKWJ  BAND DEPENDENT  SCALING OF DENSITYS TO GET K  AMOUNT          FLX  970                                                         
C   CPS IS THE STORED VALUES OF PIERLUISSI BAND MODEL COEFFIECNTS       FLX  980                                                         
C   CP1S = 10**CPS                                                      FLX  990                                                         
C   IBND MAPS BANDS TO MOLECULES                                        FLX 1000                                                         
C   DPJ REPLACES DPO  IS THE  EFFECTIVE PROBILITY BY LAYER              FLX 1010                                                         
C   TAUM IS DEFINED AS THE SUM OF THE OPTICAL DEPTHS BY MOLECULE        FLX 1020                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 1030                                                         
      DATA RUPC/50*0.0/,RUPCS/34*0.0/                                   FLX 1040                                                         
      DATA EUPS/34*0.0/,EDNS/34*0.0/                                    FLX 1050                                                         
      DATA REFS/34*0.0/,TDFS/34*0.0/                                    FLX 1060                                                         
      DATA UPFS/510*0.0/,DNFS/510*0.0/                                  FLX 1070                                                         
      DATA FAC /1.0,0.09,0.015/                                         FLX 1080                                                         
