      IF(IEMSCT .EQ. 2)THEN                                             FLX 2990                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 3000                                                         
C     CALCULATE PARAMETERS FOR SOLAR HYBRID MODIFIED                    FLX 3010                                                         
C     DELTA EDDINGTON 2-STREAM APPROXIMATION                            FLX 3020                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 3030                                                         
      SMU=CSZEN(N)                                                      FLX 3040                                                         
      B0=BETS(N)                                                        FLX 3050                                                         
