C                                                                       FLX 3080                                                         
C      OME0 TEST MAY BE MACHINE DEPENDENT                               FLX 3090                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 3100                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 3110                                                         
C      RECODED AS BS  FC AND AS*EXP(SK*X)  FOR IMPROVED                 FLX 3120                                                         
C      ACCURACY IN SOLAR FLUX CALCULATIONS FOR LARGE X                  FLX 3130                                                         
C      ( NON MACHINE DEPENDANT )                                        FLX 3140                                                         
C                                                                       FLX 3150                                                         
      G=COSBAR(N)                                                       FLX 3160                                                         
