      IF(N.EQ.1) AWCCON(M)=MDLWC                                        EXA 1840                                                         
   80 CONTINUE                                                          EXA 1850                                                         
      GO TO 185                                                         EXA 1860                                                         
100   CONTINUE                                                          EXA 1870                                                         
CCC                                                                     EXA 1880                                                         
CCC       SECTION TO LOAD EXTINCTION AND ABSORPTION COEFFICIENTS        EXA 1890                                                         
CCC       FOR CLOUD AND OR RAIN MODELS                                  EXA 1900                                                         
CCC                                                                     EXA 1910                                                         
      DO 150 N=NB,NE                                                    EXA 1920                                                         
