125   ABSC(M,N)=CCUABS(N)                                               EXA 1980                                                         
      EXTC(M,N)=CCUEXT(N)                                               EXA 1990                                                         
      ASYM(M,N)=CCUSYM(N)                                               EXA 2000                                                         
      IF(N.EQ.1) AWCCON(M)=CULWC                                        EXA 2010                                                         
      GO TO 150                                                         EXA 2020                                                         
130   ABSC(M,N)=CALABS(N)                                               EXA 2030                                                         
