      DIMENSION H1(15), H2(16), H3(13)                                  HNO  140                                                         
C     ARRAY H1 CONTAINS HNO3 ABS, COEF(CM-1ATM-1) FROM  850 TO 920 CM-1 HNO  150                                                         
      DATA H1/2.197,3.911,6.154,8.150,9.217,9.461,11.56,11.10,11.17,12.4HNO  160                                                         
     10,10.49,7.509,6.136,4.899,2.866/                                  HNO  170                                                         
