     2  .969, .995,1.000, .982, .940, .895, .937,1.000,1.075,1.143,     GMR 1480                                                         
     3  .950, .976,1.000,1.024,1.036, .932, .966,1.000,1.034,1.079,     GMR 1490                                                         
     4  .932, .966,1.000,1.034,1.068, .957, .978,1.000,1.022,1.044/     GMR 1500                                                         
      DATA FACEQ4/                                                      GMR 1510                                                         
